analysis.Summary: Vue component rendering an SVG “in use” status icon with configurable fill color
analysis.Purpose: Provide a reusable, customizable icon for order status within the application

Components.name: IconStatusInUse
Components.role: Functional Vue component that outputs an SVG icon

parameters.name: fill
parameters.description: Color value for the SVG fill attribute

analysis.Usage: Imported and used in other Vue components, e.g. import IconStatusInUse from 'modules/orders/components/icons/IconStatusInUse.vue'; then <IconStatusInUse :fill="'#ff0000'"/>
Notes: Purely functional; no reactive state or methods beyond props
Relies on CSS variable --black for default color
